-- Greece’s Solar Project Could Raise 15 Billion Euros, Welt Says
-- B y   A l e x   W e b b
-- 2012-04-15T18:11:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-15/greece-s-solar-project-could-raise-15-billion-euros-welt-says.html
Greece ’s Helios solar energy
project could raise 15 billion euros ($19.65 billion) to go
toward reducing the national debt,  Die Welt  reported in a
preview of an article to be published tomorrow, citing George Papaconstantinou, the country’s energy minister.  The project would create around 60,000 jobs, Welt cited
Papaconstantinou as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alex Webb in Munich via 
